<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Sacred
Heart Aikido Center Cebu (SHACC)<br>5<sup>th</sup>
anniversary celebration and seminar</b></font><br><small style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-style: italic;">(Schedule updated 2010 March 12. Please check back for more possible updates.)</span></small><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2"><br>The
entire Filipino and overseas Aikido community is invited to
participate in the 5<sup>th</sup> anniversary celebration  of SHACC.
Featured guest instructor is Motohiro Fukakusa Shihan, 7<sup>th</sup>
Dan Aikikai, who is Chairman and Chief Instructor of the Aikido
Association Thailand.</font></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><small><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">VENUE: <span id="lw_1268373400_0" class="yshortcuts"><span id="lw_1268373714_31" class="yshortcuts">Cebu</span></span> Midtown Hotel, Ramos Street, <span id="lw_1268373714_32" class="yshortcuts">Cebu City</span></span></small>
